Package project.exceptions

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AppointmentClashException  
    DuplicateObjectException
    DuplicateUserException is a sub-class of project.exceptions related to the attempt of adding a user that already exists in the repository to it.
    IdClashException
    States that there is a clash with the creation of an ID.
    LoginException
    An exception called when there is an error logging in to the system.
    ObjectNotFoundException
    ObjectNotFoundException is an exception thrown when an object cannot be found from a collection when it is queried.
    OutOfRangeException
    OutOfRangeException is a superclass of project.exceptions related to inputs out of a specific range, not related to indices or arrays.
    StockLevelException
    StockLevelException deal with exception related to stock levels.
